From Tom R Courtney Subject Re Space Marketing would be In some sense I think that the folks who think the idea is wonderful and the folks who want to boycott anyone who has anything to do with this project are both That is I think that space advertising is an interesting idea and if someone wants to try it out more power to However a company may discover that the cost of launch is not the only cost of advertising and a company who gauged that ill will would lose them more revenue than the advertising would gain might decide to bow out of the I got incensed when I read that Carl Sagan called this idea an I don't think that word means what he thinks it Children starving in the richest country in the world is an abomination an ad agency is at worst just in poor Tom Courtney